```catala
#[test]
declaration scope ConditionnalitéBCAE7:
  internal pixels content list of (integer, money)
  output est_arable condition
  output est_arable2 condition

scope ConditionnalitéBCAE7:
  definition pixels equals [(12, $12); (13, $14)]

  definition est_arable equals
    exists (année_pixel, pixel) among pixels such that
      année_pixel = 2025 and
      pixel >= $10

  definition est_arable2 equals
    exists (année_pixel, pixel) among
      (map each p among pixels to p.1, map each p among pixels to p.2)
    such that
      année_pixel = 2025 and
      pixel >= $10
```


```catala-test-cli
$ catala test-scope ConditionnalitéBCAE7
┌─[RESULT]─ ConditionnalitéBCAE7 ─
│ est_arable = false
│ est_arable2 = false
└─
```
